s\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作HGET和HMSET的延迟显著增加：正常时段1739ms/1573ms，异常时段9740ms/13697ms（延迟倍数5.6-8.7倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"Cart服务GetCart操作延迟异常：正常时段2260ms，异常时段9924ms-63654ms（延迟倍数4.4-28.1倍），EmptyCart操作也出现类似延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalog服务GetProduct操作延迟波动：正常时段9974ms，异常时段11696ms（延迟倍数1.2倍），但部分实例延迟降低\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结**：\n\n1. **Redis延迟是根因**：Redis的HGET和HMSET操作延迟显著增加，这是最下游的存储层异常，导致cartservice的延迟连锁反应。\n\n2. **Cart服务受影响最严重**：由于依赖Redis，cartservice的GetCart和EmptyCart操作延迟大幅增加，最高达到63654ms（正常2260ms）。\n\n3. **调用链传播路径**：Redis异常 → cartservice异常 → checkoutservice和frontend受到影响。\n\n4. **网络节点分布**：异常分布在多个K8s节点（aiops-k8s-01,03,04,05,07,08），表明是集群级别的存储层问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_processes\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod shows high error_ratio (22.0) and client_error_ratio (22.0), along with increased pod_cpu_usage (0.6) and pod_processes (2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0 -> 22.0, client_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 22.0, pod_cpu_usage: 0.0 -> 0.6, pod_processes: 1.0 -> 2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod shows high error_ratio (30.8) and client_error_ratio (30.8), along with increased pod_cpu_usage (0.6) and pod_processes (2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0 -> 30.8, clien